metadata.name: The Good, the Bad, the Ugly
metadata.description:
The Good, the Bad, the Ugly

At the moment when the sun hides behind the horizon and the city falls asleep, you can sense a peaceful tranquility and enjoy the silence. And looking at the starry sky, I know that somewhere out there, in the depths of space, is my home planet. But I keep moving, not stopping in my passionate pursuit of new travels and discoveries.  
- Blue

Original resolution: 10834  x  12500  
Tool used: Adobe Illustrator  
100% vector

1/1 artwork by Freemann
